title: Missing Sub Passengers Believed Dead After Debris Found From Likely Implosion
description: Wreckage matching the missing submersible was found by a remotely operated vehicle, and so far evidence points to a catastrophic implosion.

title: The Last AI Boom Didn't Kill Jobs. Feel Better?
description: ChatGPT is stoking fears of mass layoffs, but a study of several EU countries found the deep-learning boom of the 2010s actually created job opportunities.
